Title: Octopus Australia buys Dulacca Wind Farm
Description: Octopus Investments has made its fourth investment in Australia, acquiring the Dulacca Wind Farm from global renewable energy company RES.
Text: Octopus Australia buys Dulacca Wind Farm. Octopus Investments has made its fourth investment in Australia, acquiring the Dulacca Wind Farm from global renewable energy company RES.

Title: Brisbane couple builds tech giant on the quiet
Description: The hunt for the next Atlassian could be over after Paul and Sonia Stovell’s little-known Octopus Deploy banked one of the biggest ever local tech VC investments.
